      "instruction": "<p>Heat a pot with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>yellow</strong> <strong>mustard</strong> <strong>seeds</strong> and cook for 30 secs or until sizzling</p><p>Once sizzling, add the <strong>sliced red onion </strong>and your <strong>shredded red cabbage</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
