            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel your <strong>potatoes</strong> and chop them into small, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>potatoes</strong> to a separate pot with plenty of <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium-high and cook for 10-12 min or until fork-tender</p><p>Once done, drain and return to the pot to steam dry</p>",
      "order": 3,
