      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion and cabbage have softened, add <strong>half</strong> your <strong>cider</strong> <strong>vinegar</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) to the pot, cook for a further 30 secs then set aside to cool</p><p>Combine your <strong>mayo </strong>and<strong> Dijon mustard </strong>in a separate bowl – this is your <strong>mustard mayo</strong></p>",
