    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> pork sausage[s]</strong> to one side of a baking tray (use<strong> tin foil</strong> to avoid mess!)</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 15-20 min or until the sausage[s] is cooked through</p>",
