      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>cider</strong> <strong>vinegar</strong> to the cooled cabbage with a grind of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong> and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>chives</strong> (save the rest for garnish!) and give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> sauerkraut</strong></p><p>Cut a slit into the top of each<strong> hot dog bun</strong></p><p>Remove the tray with the sausage[s] from the oven</p><p>Add the <strong>cut</strong> <strong>hot dog bun[s]</strong> to the other side of the tray, then return the tray to the oven for 2-3 min or until warmed through</p>",
