    {
      "instruction": "<p>Fill each <strong>warmed</strong> <strong>hot</strong> <strong>dog</strong> <strong>bun</strong> with some <strong>mustard</strong> <strong>mayo</strong>, a <strong>sausage</strong> and some <strong>sauerkraut</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>sauteed</strong> <strong>potatoes</strong> to the side with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>sauerkraut </strong>and <strong>remaining mustard mayo</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>chives</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
